high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the end of the white table.
Pick up the yellow fruit that is to the left of the spoon on the white table.
Turn right and begin across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the fridge, after that turn right and walk up to the sink.
Place the yellow fruit in the larger sink basin to the right, then turn the water on, after a few seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean yellow apple.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the sink and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the clean yellow fruit inside to the right of the closest mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean yellow fruit in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the counter, turn right and move to the wall, turn right and face the table.
Turn right and move forward past the end of the table, turn left and move all the way to the fridge, turn right and move to the sink.
Place the apple in the right basin.
Turn on the faucet for 3 seconds, turn the faucet off.
Pick up the apple, turn right, move forward to the microwave, turn left and face the microwave, open the microwave door, place the apple inside, close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed apple inside the microwave.

high_descs: Slightly turn to your left then walk towards the wall and turn to your right
Pick up the potato beside the spoon on the table
Walk across the room and head to the sink
Place the potato on the sink and clean it
Get the potato on the sink
Open the microwave then heat the potato inside
anns.task_desc: Heating the clean potato in the microwave
